    <releaseNotes>
- Significant changes to concurrent monitoring design and impl, including bug fixes and code improvements related to resource usage efficiency.
- Added new concurrent monitoring setting: MaxConcurrentTasks, which applies to AppObserver, ContainerObserver and FabricSystemObserver.
- Significant performance improvements in shared utility impls.
- Removed redundant code and code that incurs too much resource cost in large service deployments (replaced with more efficient impls).
- Added more clarity to health report descriptions.
- Removed line breaks from multi-sentence health report descriptions.
- Added version check utility. FO will let you know if there is a newer version available on Github (Informational Health Event, Telemetry, ETW).
